itunes:title: JUN 27, 2022 - HUMAN EVENTS SPECIAL: POST-ROE AMERICA
title: JUN 27, 2022 - HUMAN EVENTS SPECIAL: POST-ROE AMERICA
description:
Jack Posobiec breaks down where we’re at as a country post-roe in this special episode of Human Events Daily. Starting off, riots broke out across the country over the weekend, and we’re discussing the most notable moments. Additionally, in a dystopian turn of events, large corporations are making announcements that they will pay for abortion travel costs after the Roe V. Wade decision. Pro-abortion activists across the country are calling for sex-strikes, and Texas announced $100 million spending plan to support alternatives to abortion.


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
